==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncoined
<hw>Un*coined"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
coined, or minted; <as>as, <ex>uncoined</ex> silver</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Locke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not fabricated; not artificial or counterfeit;
natural.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Plain and <xex>uncoined</xex> constancy.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncolt</ent>⟦br⟧
